  <name>Rusic</name>
  <summary>A modern, lightweight music player</summary>

  <developer id="com.temidaradev">
    <name>temidaradev</name>
  </developer>

  <description>
    <p>
      Rusic is a fast, modern music player built with Rust and the Dioxus framework.
      It scans your local music folders and organizes them into a browsable library
      by artist and album. Features include full playback controls, an immersive
      fullscreen player, dynamic theming, and system media integration. And also 
      We have Jellyfin server integration. To listen to your music from your Jellyfin server.
    </p>
    <p>
      Designed for performance and simplicity.
    </p>
  </description>

